title: FreedomEV 2.0
subtitle: From Tesla Hacking to a free mobility stack
abstract:
Last year the FreedomEV project was launched as an addon to the existing software for the older Tesla Model S and Tesla Model X cars.

FreedomEV envisions a future without mass surveillance, with full control over our own car.

Today we launch FreedomEV 2.0. More features, more supported cars and where we are now.

Let us play with our car!
